quran[6{c,v,t}:
9,1,elaan baraat hai Allah aur is ke rasool ki taraf se unn mushriqeen ko jin se tum ne muahiday kiye thay
9,2,"pas tum log malik mein chaar mahinay aur chal phir lau aur jaan rakho ke tum Allah ko aajiz karne walay nahi ho, aur yeh ke Allah munkareen haq ko ruswa karne wala hai"
9,3,"ittila aam hai Allah aur is ke rasool ki taraf se hajj akbar ke din tamam logon ke liye ke Allah mushriqeen se buri alzmh hai aur uss ka rasool bhi ab agar tum log tauba kar lau to tumahray hi liye behtar hai aur jo mun phertey ho to khoob samajh lau ke tum Allah ko aajiz karne walay nahi ho aur ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, inkaar karne walon ko sakht azaab ki khushkhabri suna do"
9,4,"bajuz unn mushriqeen ke jin se tum ne maahd y kiye phir unhon ne apne ehad ko poora karne mein tumahray sath koi kami nahi ki aur nah tumahray khilaaf kisi ki madad ki, to aisay logon ke sath tum bhi muddat moahida taq wafa karo kyunkay Allah Muttaqiyun hi ko pasand karta hai"
9,5,pas jab haraam mahinay guzar jayen to mushriqeen ko qatal karo jahan pao aur inhen pakro aur ghaayro aur har ghaat mein unn ki khabar lainay ke liye betho phir agar woh tauba kar len aur namaz qaim karen aur zkoh den to inhen chore do Allah dar guzar karne wala aur reham frmane wala hai
9,6,aur agar mushriqeen mein se koi shakhs panah maang kar tumahray paas aana chahay ( taakay Allah ka kalaam sunay ) to ussay panah day do yahan taq ke woh Allah ka kalaam sun le phir ussay is kemaman (mehfooz jagah) taq pouncha do yeh is liye karna chahiye ke yeh log ilm nahi rakhtay
